u88fd\u54c1\u300cEFP01\u300dPMIC\u30b7\u30ea\u30fc\u30ba\u3092\u767a\u8868\u30bf\u30fc\u30f3\u30ad\u30fcPMIC\u30bd\u30ea\u30e5\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u304c\u3001\u30a2\u30af\u30c6\u30a3\u30d6\u96fb\u6d41\u3068\u30b9\u30ea\u30fc\u30d7\u96fb\u6d41\u3092\u6700\u592750</p>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://t.co/qebYqkLaOu"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/3dLEoTlI.jpg"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258854212001083392", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/siliconlabs/status/1258854212001083392", "author": "Silicon Labs", "time": 1588969207, "timeFormatted": "May 8", "text": "<h2 class=\"TwitterCard-title js-cardClick tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">Electronic Design in the Age of COVID-19 - Engineering Podcast</h2>\n<p class=\"tcu-resetMargin u-block TwitterCardsGrid-col--spacerTop tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">In the face of the most severe pandemic in a century, how are electrical engineers dealing with the challenge of working from home? Here are three stories of engineering success in spite of separat...</p>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://t.co/mxXlS2KhVd"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/UuSDOx-z.png"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258819319749840898", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/siliconlabs/status/1258819319749840898", "author": "Silicon Labs", "time": 1588960888, "timeFormatted": "May 8", "text": "Learn how you can supercharge beacons with Bluetooth 5.0 from our blog post and whitepaper: <a class=\"twitter-timeline-link\" data-expanded-url=\"https://bit.ly/2SOie9R\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://t.co/lhm7u1HQv2\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bit.ly/2SOie9R\"><span class=\"tco-ellipsis\"></span><span class=\"js-display-url\">bit.ly/2SOie9R</span><span class=\"tco-ellipsis\"></span></a> <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/bluetoothbeacons?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>bluetoothbeacons</b></a> <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/bluetooth5?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>bluetooth5</b></a> <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BLE?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>BLE</b></a>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://bit.ly/2SOie9R"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/ixEv_g0T_bigger.png"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258422890145423366", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/EEWorldOnline/status/1258422890145423366", "author": "EE World", "time": 1588866372, "timeFormatted": "May 7", "text": "<h2 class=\"TwitterCard-title js-cardClick tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">Power-management ICs cut active and sleep current by up to 50%</h2>\n<p class=\"tcu-resetMargin u-block TwitterCardsGrid-col--spacerTop tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">Silicon Labs announces a new line of energy-friendly power management ICs (PMICs) serving as dedicated companion chips for&nbsp;EFR32 wireless devices&nbsp;and&nbsp;EFM32 microcontrollers&nbsp;(MCUs). The&nbsp;EFP01 PMIC...</p>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://t.co/CPzDVveS7s"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/5loAxr_i.jpg"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258481756560404488", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/siliconlabs/status/1258481756560404488", "author": "Silicon Labs", "time": 1588880406, "timeFormatted": "May 7", "text": "Learn how our Secure Vault technology makes it easier for <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IoT?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>IoT</b></a> product manufacturers to protect their brand, product designs, and consumer data. Join our webinar on May 13: <a class=\"twitter-timeline-link\" data-expanded-url=\"https://bit.ly/2YK3cGa\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://t.co/8gN9Lk6rpe\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bit.ly/2YK3cGa\"><span class=\"tco-ellipsis\"></span><span class=\"js-display-url\">bit.ly/2YK3cGa</span><span class=\"tco-ellipsis\"></span></a> <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IoTsecurity?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>IoTsecurity</b></a>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://bit.ly/2YK3cGa"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/EXcGfN-WsAAItG8.jpg"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258442788078747648", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/siliconlabs/status/1258442788078747648", "author": "Silicon Labs", "time": 1588871116, "timeFormatted": "May 7", "text": "<h2 class=\"TwitterCard-title js-cardClick tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">Join the #ieatlocal Challenge</h2>\n<p class=\"tcu-resetMargin u-block TwitterCardsGrid-col--spacerTop tcu-textEllipse--multiline\" dir=\"ltr\">Tyson Tuttle, CEO of Silicon Labs and Bobby Jenkins, Owner of ABC Home &amp; Commercial are the leading way in supporting local restaurants.</p>", "entries": {"urls": ["https://bit.ly/2WbM7D3"], "photos": ["https://news.platformio.org/tweets/siliconlabs/vd00ESEZ.png"]}, "isPinned": false}, {"tweetId": "1258366122300264448", "tweetUrl": "https://twitter.com/siliconlabs/status/1258366122300264448", "author": "Silicon Labs", "time": 1588852837, "timeFormatted": "May 7", "text": "At a time when we are choosing between risking our lives to keep economic wheels spinning or paralyzing our productive means to quarantine and stay safe, the <a class=\"twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav\" data-query-source=\"hashtag_click\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IoT?src=hash\"><s>#</s><b>IoT</b></a> can provide a third favorable option: <a class=\"twitter-timeline-link\" data-expanded-url=\"https://bit.ly/3fsjb1g\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://t.co/B1u9OWbqCk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https